nodes.text: Dee Bradley Baker is an American voice actor who worked on the Star Wars: The Clone Wars film and TV series, voicing all clone troopers and many other characters, as well as voicing Ilco Munica in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens. He voices the members of Clone Force 99 in Star Wars: The Bad Batch.
